SCARY FAST SMILE was five wide on the turn and no factor. SAM SEZ vied for the lead while inside into the turn, was used up then stopped. A steward's inquiry was held concerning the run in deep stretch. Also a claim of foul was lodged by the rider of RASSLER for interference in deep stretch. After reviewing the film's, no action was taken.
